description:
Kipper is someone who would be fun to sit around and smoke a joint with. This 20-year-old is very laid back and quite philosophical.

He just got out of a relationship with a girl, but said he's been with both guys and girls. He places himself at 50/50 on the gay/straight scale.

"I'm just trying to sort things out right now," he said.

That's what your twenties are for!
title: Kipper
